      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORE THAN WORDS (1) clocked a respectable 25.95 when placed over 460m at Warragul last start in a Grade 5. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. SOPHIE BANJO (3) filled a minor placing last start at Traralgon behind Carry On Maci (20.05) in a Grade 4/5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Leading player again. MATILDA ROSE (8) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish second, beaten 6 lengths (24.49) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 435m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Overdue and expected to feature again. PAW ALLESANDRA (2) generally performs well over this distance.",
